* Iron Raptor could taste the mech fluid of FireBlade touch her tongue.
And slowly, the inner jaws from the roof of her mouth crept towards the arm 
that we trapped by her teeth.
But her head was almost pulled back by FireBlade as he pulled, so her neck 
strained to keep pulling her own way.
Luckily, this time, her tail had moved out of the way of FireBlades sword, 
gicing it tome to heal.  And that's just what it did.
The armor/skin began to fuse together as she concintrated on mending the 
wound.
The inner jaws finally slammed down to get a further lock on his arm, 
pulling back and biting again, only to pull back a second time.  Ripping and 
mutilating.
Iron Raptor's black eyes suddenly focused on the movement of FireBlade's 
shoulder mounted grenade launcher, suddenly pushing forward and opening her 
mouth more so that she could get the whole of his shoulder into it.
She slammed her head down onto him, hoping that he would fall and she could 
maul him from there.
But one of her arms came up and tried to grab the arm with the sword.*

" Not as easily won over as you though, am I?!"
